Package library

Class Publication

java.lang.Object
library.Publication
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Publication>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Blueray, Book, Magazine
public class Publication
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Publication>
Abstract class to represent publications held in a library. Implements Comparable so that Publications can be sorted/searched.
Author:
George Paul
